{
  "texts": [
    "Note: This figure compares the results of the streetlight experiment when using AI agents versus human subjects.",
    "In Panel A, the outcome of interest is the average group earnings (as a percentage of the maximum possible earnings).",
    "In Panel B, the outcome of interest is the mean likelihood of a breakthrough, which occurs when at least one group member finds the diamond.",
    "Plots i) show the results obtained in the original lab experiment using human subjects, while plots ii) show the results obtained from the simulated experiments using AI agents.",
    "How closely do AI agents mimic this strategic behavior?"
  ]
}